  <data name="HowToUseText" xml:space="preserve"><value>Atempause runs quietly in your system tray (☯ icon).

How it works:
• At random intervals, your screen fades to black for a few seconds
• A gong sounds at the start and end of each break
• Use this pause to breathe, close your eyes, and reset

Controls:
• ESC — dismiss a break early (unless Handcuffs mode is on)
• Snooze — temporarily pause from the system tray
• Settings — configure timing, visuals, and sounds

The app detects active camera/microphone usage and will skip breaks during video calls.</value></data>
